snippet.textDisplay:
Sanwariyo ghat mai re, Ramaiyo ghat mai (English: Sanwariya (Sanwariya Means Lord krishna for Meera /her Husband) is in my heart, Ram (Lord Ram) is in my heart)  Sanwariyo ghat mai re, Ramaiyo ghat mai Thaane kattey, thaane kattey (where are you ) Thaane kattey, thaane kattey Thaane kattey dhoondba jaaun re (English: where should I go to find you?) Sanwariyo ghat mai, (English: My Love is in my Heart) Ho.. o... Jiyo....

Birhma dekhya Bishnu dekhya (English: I've Seen Lord Brahma, seen Lord Vishnu) Birhma dekhya Bishnu dekhya (English: And have seen Goddess Saraswati)  Dekhi Sarosat maai re.. Dekhi Sarosat maai re.. Sanwariyo ghat mai Thaane kattey, thaane kattey Thaane kattey, thaane kattey Thaane kattey hawaalva jaaun re Sanwariyo ghat maa Ho.. o... Jiyo....

Its a Rajasthani folk/bhajan based on Meera’s search of Lord krishna
